---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Disclaimer - ToolVerse"
  description="Legal disclaimer regarding the accuracy, performance and usage of outputs generated by ToolVerse utilities."
>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto glass-card p-6 sm:p-8 rounded-3xl space-y-6">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-text-main border-b border-border-card pb-3">Legal Disclaimer</h1>
    <p class="text-xs text-text-muted">Last Updated: July 3, 2026</p>

    <section class="space-y-3">
      <h2 class="text-base font-bold text-text-main">Accuracy of Results</h2>
      <p class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
        The tool outputs, formatters, code playground compilations, and converters provided on ToolVerse.com are generated client-side by algorithms. While we strive for accuracy, bugs or differences in engine implementation may occur. Users should cross-reference and test outputs before deploying to production systems.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-3">
      <h2 class="text-base font-bold text-text-main">Artificial Intelligence disclaimer</h2>
      <p class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
        Our AI features process queries using Google Gemini API or simulation modes. The AI model outputs may contain inaccuracies, hallucinations, or obsolete syntax. ToolVerse is not responsible for the quality, security, or security compliance of AI-suggested code.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-3">
      <h2 class="text-base font-bold text-text-main">Local Security Notice</h2>
      <p class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
        Because execution happens entirely inside your browser container, any data leaked via physical device compromises or malicious browser extensions is outside our scope of control. Secure your workspace endpoint regularly.
      </p>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>
